            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              Heights are measured in shoes at most parks
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              Some parks offer height wristbands at entrance
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              Requirements can change — verify day-of
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">At the Park</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
